1
00:00:32,240 --> 00:00:33,640
I knew you would be here.

2
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:38,860
Xia Xue's phone is off.

3
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:41,310
I'm worried something happened to her.

4
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:44,170
I came because I was worried
about Xia Xue too.

5
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,840
I suspect Hou Jun hid her.

6
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:50,520
Officer Qin.

7
00:00:51,070 --> 00:00:52,150
I hope the police

8
00:00:52,430 --> 00:00:54,030
can ensure Xia Xue's safety.

9
00:00:56,000 --> 00:00:57,030
The news says

10
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,670
Ma Derong is dead.

11
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,320
Now,

12
00:01:04,709 --> 00:01:06,280
there's no one left to prove

13
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:10,770
that Hou Jun was the mastermind
behind Hou Shanshan's kidnapping.

14
00:01:11,590 --> 00:01:12,430
That's right.

15
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,120
But Hou Jun's recent actions

16
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:16,780
all show that he's panicking.

17
00:01:16,950 --> 00:01:19,070
People make mistakes when they panic.

18
00:01:19,070 --> 00:01:21,230
So I believe we'll find evidence soon.

19
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,230
Officer Qin,

20
00:01:24,590 --> 00:01:25,720
I'm counting on you.

21
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,230
Lu Ming.

22
00:01:30,430 --> 00:01:32,360
Don't forget what you promised me.

23
00:01:35,039 --> 00:01:35,870
Soon.

24
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,470
Mr. Hou.

25
00:03:25,030 --> 00:03:25,840
How did it go?

26
00:03:26,360 --> 00:03:27,620
There's been trouble.

27
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,190
Ma Derong was beaten to death by Biao,

28
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:31,400
and Hou Shanshan
was rescued by the police.

29
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,000
How the hell did this happen?

30
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,870
We were just paid to do a job.

31
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:38,850
I really didn't know
about Li Biao's other stuff.

32
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:41,240
Then do you know who Li Biao worked for?

33
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,030
No.

34
00:03:42,310 --> 00:03:43,590
Every time he made a call,

35
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:45,150
he just called the person "boss."

36
00:03:45,150 --> 00:03:47,590
Who the boss was, I don't know.

37
00:03:49,520 --> 00:03:51,590
Since Ma Derong is a dead end,

38
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,960
let's proceed with our previous plan.

39
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,690
Understood.

40
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,150
I've already arranged it.

41
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:58,079
As long as you take your daughter
out of the country,

42
00:03:58,079 --> 00:03:59,360
and have her sign

43
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,800
a waiver of beneficiary rights abroad,

44
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:01,870
the money in her account

45
00:04:01,870 --> 00:04:04,330
can be legally transferred
to your account.

46
00:04:08,710 --> 00:04:10,590
Are all the arrangements overseas
in place?

47
00:04:10,590 --> 00:04:11,800
Everything's been arranged.

48
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,750
These are for your family of three.

49
00:04:13,750 --> 00:04:15,550
Tickets, passports, and visas.

50
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,310
Alright.

51
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:35,430
Ren Yi, how are things on your end?

52
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:37,230
Did you get anything out of them?

53
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:39,600
Nothing at all.

54
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,800
Did you check the call records?

55
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,870
They're all burner numbers.

56
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:43,270
What about the finances?

57
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,510
You're awake. How are you feeling?

58
00:05:05,510 --> 00:05:07,190
Do you feel any discomfort?

59
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:11,390
Auntie, I want to see my mom.

60
00:05:12,870 --> 00:05:14,160
Get some rest first.

61
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:16,040
Your mom will come see you soon.

62
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,850
Let's sit up and have some water, okay?

63
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:20,360
Come on. Up you go.

64
00:05:23,270 --> 00:05:24,270
Here. Slowly.

65
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:38,050
Let me know if you want anything to eat.

66
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,480
Mr. Hou.

67
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,960
Let's leave together tomorrow.

68
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:25,390
Where to?

69
00:06:26,270 --> 00:06:28,510
To a place where no one knows us.

70
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:33,159
I won't go with you.

71
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,840
I'm afraid it's not up to you.

72
00:06:38,310 --> 00:06:39,510
I already got the DV

73
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,600
from Ma Derong.

74
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:44,310
I'll give you one last chance to choose.

75
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:45,870
You can come with me

76
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:47,400
and say goodbye to the past.

77
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:50,190
We can live a peaceful life
with Shanshan.

78
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:52,950
Of course, you can choose
to stay in Nanping.

79
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:55,240
But I'll let the whole world know

80
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:56,570
that you are a murderer.

81
00:06:57,920 --> 00:06:59,830
Like a rat in the street,

82
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:01,870
you'll be despised by everyone.

83
00:07:01,870 --> 00:07:03,480
And Shanshan — that child

84
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,720
will never escape the fate

85
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:08,580
of being a murderer's child
for the rest of her life.

86
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,240
Hello.

87
00:07:21,120 --> 00:07:21,830
Mr. Hou,

88
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,600
Mr. Yang has drafted
the overseas acquisition contract.

89
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,040
You need to come and review it.

90
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,680
Once you sign this contract,

91
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,480
all your domestic assets

92
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,630
will be automatically transferred
overseas.

93
00:07:31,630 --> 00:07:32,680
Okay, got it.

94
00:07:40,870 --> 00:07:42,310
You can leave anytime.

95
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:46,150
As for what to choose,

96
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,600
that's for you to weigh.

97
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:04,000
If she wants to leave, don't stop her.

98
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:05,000
Yes, sir.

99
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,310
Hello, Lu Ming.

100
00:08:24,510 --> 00:08:26,630
Can you pick me up
at the abandoned villa in Guanshan?

101
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:27,680
Are you okay?

102
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,040
I'm fine.

103
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,840
How's Shanshan?

104
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,600
The police are protecting Shanshan.

105
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,960
She's a bit shaken.

106
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,420
She's at the hospital now.

107
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,790
Ma Derong is dead.

108
00:08:53,320 --> 00:08:55,030
He was killed by Hou Jun's men

109
00:08:55,030 --> 00:08:56,760
while trying to save Shanshan.

110
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:58,190
When the police arrived,

111
00:08:58,750 --> 00:08:59,950
he was already dying.

112
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,790
The men who kidnapped Shanshan were

113
00:09:06,510 --> 00:09:07,790
Wang Bingkun

114
00:09:07,790 --> 00:09:08,960
and Biao,

115
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,670
who are both dead.

116
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:16,030
Is there really no evidence

117
00:09:16,150 --> 00:09:17,630
that Hou Jun ordered it?

118
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,840
If a crime was committed,

119
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,440
there will be evidence.

120
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,200
We just haven't found it yet.

121
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,390
Don't worry.

122
00:09:32,030 --> 00:09:33,670
We'll find a way.

123
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,790
Thank you.

124
00:10:20,150 --> 00:10:21,200
Mom!

125
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:23,550
Sweetheart.

126
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:25,750
Are you okay?

127
00:10:25,750 --> 00:10:26,910
Where are you hurt?

128
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:31,910
You're okay? You look fine to me.

129
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:33,320
Don't worry.

130
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:35,000
We did a full checkup.

131
00:10:35,000 --> 00:10:36,390
Apart from a scraped knee,

132
00:10:36,390 --> 00:10:37,510
she's fine.

133
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:42,150
You're so brave, sweetheart.

134
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,120
Does it hurt?

135
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:44,510
No.

136
00:10:44,550 --> 00:10:45,440
No.

137
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,030
That's good.

138
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:56,480
Xia Xue has arrived at the hospital.

139
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:59,120
Hou Jun letting her go so easily

140
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,820
means something's wrong.

141
00:11:00,870 --> 00:11:01,440
Also,

142
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:04,080
I found out Hou Jun
is transferring assets overseas

143
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:06,600
since he holds Shanshan's trust fund.

144
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,240
But these are just your guesses.

145
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,790
If we want to arrest him,

146
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,750
we need more evidence.

147
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:20,510
Thank you.

148
00:11:20,750 --> 00:11:21,480
You're welcome.

149
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:22,630
It's our duty.

150
00:11:24,550 --> 00:11:25,440
Xia Xue,

151
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:28,030
if you know any evidence
of Hou Jun's crimes,

152
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:30,360
please provide it promptly.

153
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,870
You can come with me

154
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,400
and say goodbye to the past.

155
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:44,200
We can live a peaceful life with Shanshan.

156
00:11:44,480 --> 00:11:46,940
Of course, you can choose
to stay in Nanping.

157
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:48,790
But I'll let the whole world

158
00:11:48,790 --> 00:11:50,440
know that you are a murderer.

159
00:11:51,910 --> 00:11:53,670
Like a rat in the street,

160
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,880
you'll be despised by everyone.

161
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:58,080
And Shanshan — that child

162
00:11:58,720 --> 00:12:00,200
will never escape the fate

163
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:03,060
of being a murderer's child
for the rest of her life.

164
00:12:26,870 --> 00:12:29,030
Is there really no evidence

165
00:12:29,200 --> 00:12:30,530
that Hou Jun ordered it?

166
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:36,440
Don't worry.

167
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,670
We'll find a way.

168
00:12:54,910 --> 00:12:55,790
Hello?

169
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,030
Hello? Lu Ming?

170
00:13:04,150 --> 00:13:05,790
Do you have a new lead?

171
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:07,200
Officer Qin.

172
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,330
I've caused you trouble

173
00:13:11,870 --> 00:13:13,200
over the years.

174
00:13:15,270 --> 00:13:16,390
Lu Ming, don't say this now.

175
00:13:16,390 --> 00:13:16,960
Listen to me.

176
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,440
Don't do anything stupid.

177
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:20,870
I killed Ma Ke.

178
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:23,480
There's a big rock under Nanping Bridge.

179
00:13:23,480 --> 00:13:25,280
His remains are buried under it.

180
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:29,570
I'm in an abandoned plane
in the western suburbs.

181
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,510
Don't hang up.

182
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,440
Qiao.

183
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:40,350
Grab the recording equipment
and come with me.

184
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,270
Nice atmosphere.

185
00:14:43,270 --> 00:14:44,790
You picked such a dump.

186
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,380
Where's Shanshan?

187
00:14:49,870 --> 00:14:51,150
I brought the DV.

188
00:14:51,150 --> 00:14:52,080
What Shanshan?

189
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:55,200
What do you mean?

190
00:15:04,270 --> 00:15:05,270
Hou Jun,

191
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,610
I'll point you to a way out.

192
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:11,030
Turn yourself in.

193
00:15:11,670 --> 00:15:14,070
Take responsibility for what you've done.

194
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:22,150
I really don't know
what you're talking about.

195
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,970
Stop playing dumb, Hou Jun.

196
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,190
I've already confessed.

197
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:30,630
I killed Ma Ke.

198
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:32,510
I buried the body too.

199
00:15:33,750 --> 00:15:36,010
So you also need to bear the consequences

200
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,400
for what you've done.

201
00:15:43,870 --> 00:15:45,730
What consequences should I bear?

202
00:15:48,440 --> 00:15:49,970
I'm a law-abiding citizen.

203
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:01,440
Lu Ming.

204
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:04,390
There's one thing

205
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:07,030
that I really can't figure out.

206
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,790
Help me analyze it.

207
00:16:10,390 --> 00:16:12,720
Xia Xue and I
have been married for 8 years.

208
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:15,380
You and her split nearly 10 years ago.

209
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:18,080
Yet you still can't forget her.

210
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:21,000
Do you love her that much?

211
00:16:29,720 --> 00:16:31,580
Since you've already confessed,

212
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:35,000
then this DV

213
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:37,000
can't threaten you anymore, right?

214
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:42,000
Then I have no choice
but to post it online.

215
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:43,790
Then everyone will know

216
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,270
that Xia Xue is a murderer.

217
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:51,270
She’ll become a topic of gossip for people

218
00:16:51,750 --> 00:16:52,880
across the country.

219
00:16:57,440 --> 00:17:00,960
What kind of life
do you think she'll have then?

220
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:02,750
You've done so much

221
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:05,589
just so Xia Xue could start over,
haven't you?

222
00:17:05,589 --> 00:17:06,960
Let me tell you, Lu Ming.

223
00:17:07,270 --> 00:17:08,400
For the rest of her life,

224
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,440
every day,

225
00:17:10,510 --> 00:17:12,200
every minute, every second,

226
00:17:13,349 --> 00:17:16,400
she'll live under everyone's scrutiny.

227
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,960
What can you do then?

228
00:17:21,069 --> 00:17:23,160
You can only watch helplessly.

229
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:25,410
There's nothing you can do.

230
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:33,960
That hurts!

231
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:39,750
What?

232
00:17:40,480 --> 00:17:41,960
Can't take it already?

233
00:17:45,590 --> 00:17:47,240
And Hou Shanshan too.

234
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:54,560
Shanshan will meet
the same fate as Xia Xue.

235
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,200
She will know

236
00:17:57,960 --> 00:18:00,680
that she is the child
of a murderer and a rapist.

237
00:18:01,070 --> 00:18:03,000
Her teachers and her classmates

238
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:04,680
will stay away from her.

239
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:07,300
She will become a laughingstock.

240
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:09,880
She will doubt her life from then on.

241
00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:11,590
She will hate her mother!

242
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:16,160
She'll hate everyone in this world.

243
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,680
All of this

244
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:23,960
was caused by you guys.

245
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,200
When that day comes,

246
00:18:29,480 --> 00:18:31,440
will you still dare to threaten me?

247
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,830
Look forward, Lu Ming.

248
00:18:44,880 --> 00:18:47,350
Xia Xue can only live in your memories.

249
00:18:47,830 --> 00:18:48,960
Wake up.

250
00:18:55,240 --> 00:18:56,640
Mr. Yang, I heard the two companies have

251
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,960
entered the final stage of acquisition.

252
00:18:57,960 --> 00:18:59,070
May I ask why you're suddenly holding

253
00:18:59,070 --> 00:19:00,160
this press conference now?

254
00:19:00,160 --> 00:19:01,440
Mr. Yang! Mr. Yang!

255
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:04,880
Is this how you pushed Liu Zhijun

256
00:19:04,880 --> 00:19:06,720
step by step, to his death?

257
00:19:09,350 --> 00:19:11,400
Do you really think no one knows

258
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,830
about the dirty things you did back then?

259
00:19:12,830 --> 00:19:15,030
Liu Zhijun said you were the mastermind

260
00:19:15,030 --> 00:19:17,230
behind the shipyard explosion, right?

261
00:19:19,400 --> 00:19:20,800
You're trying to trap me.

262
00:19:22,350 --> 00:19:24,000
I won't fall for your tricks.

263
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:32,200
Hello, Mr. Yang?

264
00:19:32,270 --> 00:19:33,200
Hou Jun.

265
00:19:33,200 --> 00:19:36,070
Our partnership
on the overseas acquisition ends here.

266
00:19:36,070 --> 00:19:37,790
Your wife has exposed
the shipyard explosion

267
00:19:37,790 --> 00:19:38,960
to the media.

268
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:40,640
Good luck to you.

269
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:42,440
Mr. Yang. Mr-

270
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:47,510
How you do business
is how you are as a person.

271
00:19:47,510 --> 00:19:48,830
Integrity comes first.

272
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,480
We not only look at the partner company's

273
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:51,640
future potential,

274
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,350
but also the character and ethics

275
00:19:53,350 --> 00:19:54,750
of the person in charge.

276
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:56,720
Just now,

277
00:19:57,160 --> 00:19:58,640
we received a tip-off.

278
00:19:58,920 --> 00:20:00,960
Hou Jun, the head of the partner company,

279
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:04,160
is likely connected
to the shipyard explosion years ago.

280
00:20:04,440 --> 00:20:06,590
We are currently suspending

281
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:08,550
all cooperation with the shipyard.

282
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:10,350
The ongoing overseas acquisition plan

283
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:13,070
is also suspended, effective immediately.

284
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:14,750
Once the police uncover the truth,

285
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:16,350
we will discuss next steps.

286
00:20:31,720 --> 00:20:33,790
Xia Xue chose you after all.

287
00:20:36,240 --> 00:20:37,000
Hou Jun.

288
00:20:38,590 --> 00:20:39,920
Everything is over now.

289
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,440
Are you going to

290
00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:44,480
atone for the people
who died in the shipyard explosion?

291
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,940
What do I have to atone for?

292
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:48,310
That shipyard explosion

293
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:50,440
was orchestrated by Liu Zhijun!

294
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:52,200
I took him out.

295
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,680
I killed him!

296
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:59,320
Doesn't that count
as justice for the victims?

297
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,110
Lu Ming, let me ask you.

298
00:21:01,110 --> 00:21:03,270
Is there such a thing
as a good person in this world?

299
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:05,830
Are Liu Zhijun and Ma Derong good people?

300
00:21:06,480 --> 00:21:07,750
All I did

301
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:10,110
was to avenge
those who were harmed by them.

302
00:21:10,110 --> 00:21:11,640
What did I do wrong?

303
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:13,440
Have you forgotten?

304
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:15,810
Have you forgotten how they treated you?

305
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,960
If it weren't for me,

306
00:21:18,160 --> 00:21:20,000
if I hadn't helped submit
those materials for you,

307
00:21:20,000 --> 00:21:21,800
would you be where you are today?

308
00:21:30,070 --> 00:21:32,430
I'll always be grateful
for what you did back then.

309
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:34,030
Thank you for saving Xia Xue.

310
00:21:34,960 --> 00:21:35,960
But Hou Jun,

311
00:21:37,240 --> 00:21:39,370
that doesn't mean we can
escape the law

312
00:21:39,510 --> 00:21:41,590
after hurting others.

313
00:21:42,640 --> 00:21:43,880
Wrong is wrong.

314
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,750
Not just you.

315
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:49,260
All of us must take
responsibility for what we've done.

316
00:21:50,640 --> 00:21:51,970
I've called the police.

317
00:21:52,830 --> 00:21:54,490
Let's wait for them together.

318
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:09,070
We worked so well together before.

319
00:22:11,270 --> 00:22:13,160
How did it end up like this?

320
00:22:15,350 --> 00:22:16,640
It's all over.

321
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:33,060
What's the situation on your end?

322
00:22:37,030 --> 00:22:38,030
Hou Jun.

323
00:22:38,830 --> 00:22:40,590
I have evidence that you killed.

324
00:22:40,590 --> 00:22:42,550
I don't care what evidence you have.

325
00:22:42,550 --> 00:22:44,160
Go to hell!

326
00:23:15,590 --> 00:23:16,680
All units, attention.

327
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:17,920
There may be a hostage on the plane

328
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:19,520
held by the suspect, Hou Jun.

329
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,740
Please ensure the hostage's safety.

330
00:24:12,510 --> 00:24:13,680
Hands up!

331
00:24:42,510 --> 00:24:45,000
Lu Ming! Lu Ming, wake up.

332
00:25:06,270 --> 00:25:08,160
Call an ambulance!

333
00:25:29,680 --> 00:25:31,740
Stay back. This is a restricted area.

334
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:28,680
Dig.

335
00:26:39,400 --> 00:26:41,200
Boss, we found it.

336
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:44,440
It's been buried so long,
the body must be highly decomposed.

337
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:46,590
Contact forensics immediately. Rush this.

338
00:26:46,590 --> 00:26:47,480
Copy that.

339
00:26:49,750 --> 00:26:51,830
Forensics is analyzing the body.

340
00:26:52,000 --> 00:26:55,200
The videotape has also been sent to
the tech department for verification.

341
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,800
We have statements
from Lu Ming and Hou Jun too.

342
00:26:57,960 --> 00:26:59,480
If everything lines up,

343
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,760
we should be able to close the case.

344
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,000
Hello?

345
00:27:14,590 --> 00:27:15,550
Officer Qin,

346
00:27:16,880 --> 00:27:18,070
let's meet.

347
00:27:53,160 --> 00:27:54,960
What will Hou Jun's sentence be?

348
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:58,590
If nothing unexpected happens,

349
00:28:00,920 --> 00:28:01,980
the death penalty.

350
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:20,240
Officer Qin.

351
00:28:23,310 --> 00:28:24,200
That day,

352
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:28,550
when Lu Ming drove me to the hospital,

353
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:31,030
it felt like

354
00:28:31,350 --> 00:28:32,750
the drive took forever.

355
00:28:34,310 --> 00:28:36,240
We didn't really talk much.

356
00:28:39,070 --> 00:28:39,960
But...

357
00:28:44,350 --> 00:28:46,200
I really wanted to ask him a question,

358
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,200
which was,

359
00:28:48,070 --> 00:28:49,350
after all these years,

360
00:28:51,960 --> 00:28:53,490
have you ever regretted it?

361
00:28:58,440 --> 00:28:59,640
But I didn't ask.

362
00:29:00,880 --> 00:29:02,440
I just said,

363
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:04,110
thank you.

364
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:10,200
But thinking back now,

365
00:29:10,830 --> 00:29:12,680
I'm glad I said thank you.

366
00:29:17,830 --> 00:29:19,440
Actually, Lu Ming and I

367
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:22,640
are quite alike.

368
00:29:23,790 --> 00:29:25,650
We've always done what we thought

369
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:28,400
was best for the other.

370
00:29:30,550 --> 00:29:31,920
Just like this time.

371
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:34,000
He...

372
00:29:36,440 --> 00:29:38,000
thought if he died,

373
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:43,200
I could live a good life.

374
00:29:55,590 --> 00:29:56,640
Officer Qin.

375
00:30:05,680 --> 00:30:06,960
I killed Ma Ke.

376
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:34,040
Captain Qin.

377
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:36,590
Forensics has determined the cause
of Ma Ke's death.

378
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:37,830
The right cervical vertebra

379
00:30:37,830 --> 00:30:39,920
shows signs of a stab wound
from a sharp conical object,

380
00:30:39,920 --> 00:30:42,120
possibly injuring the carotid artery.

381
00:31:15,110 --> 00:31:16,160
Forensics concluded

382
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,240
Ma Ke's cause of death

383
00:31:17,240 --> 00:31:19,110
was acute hemorrhagic shock.

384
00:31:19,960 --> 00:31:21,510
The fight exacerbated the bleeding

385
00:31:21,510 --> 00:31:22,840
and hastened his death.

386
00:31:25,750 --> 00:31:26,830
Ma Ke

387
00:31:27,110 --> 00:31:28,590
raped me.

388
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,960
I study law.

389
00:31:33,310 --> 00:31:35,160
Huacheng University Law School.

390
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,000
Officer Qin Wen.

391
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:37,790
In the future, maybe we could

392
00:31:37,790 --> 00:31:39,250
uphold justice together.

393
00:31:46,680 --> 00:31:48,610
I've said everything I need to say.

394
00:31:49,720 --> 00:31:51,960
I have nothing more to add.

395
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:56,800
I didn't come here
to ask you questions today.

396
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:59,590
I came to tell you something.

397
00:32:11,510 --> 00:32:12,680
How did he die?

398
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:17,200
He was killed by Hou Jun

399
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:20,000
while trying to obtain evidence
of Hou Jun's crimes.

400
00:32:20,000 --> 00:32:20,720
Also,

401
00:32:21,200 --> 00:32:23,480
Xia Xue has confessed
that she killed Ma Ke.

402
00:32:23,480 --> 00:32:25,540
We have sufficient evidence as well.

403
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:28,540
Are you sure you want to stick
to this statement?

404
00:32:34,350 --> 00:32:35,640
Officer Qin.

405
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:38,440
I'd like to ask you a favor.

406
00:32:39,480 --> 00:32:41,480
Please take care of Shanshan for me.

407
00:32:41,960 --> 00:32:44,110
Don't worry. I will.

408
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:46,240
Thank you.

409
00:33:17,510 --> 00:33:19,310
Sign at the bottom right corner.

410
00:33:37,750 --> 00:33:39,150
You have to take that off.

411
00:33:41,070 --> 00:33:43,200
The ring on your finger has to come off.

412
00:35:07,710 --> 00:35:09,360
We are friends forever.

413
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,090
Nothing will ever change that.

414
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:13,000
September 4th, 2003.

415
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,550
Xia Xue,

416
00:38:15,190 --> 00:38:17,250
I'm listening to your favorite song.

417
00:38:36,360 --> 00:38:37,960
If only you were here.

418
00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:41,880
I really miss the days
when we shared one pair of earphones

419
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,680
and listened to music together.

420
00:38:45,960 --> 00:38:50,840
Today is February 29th, 2004.

421
00:38:51,710 --> 00:38:54,110
It's the 1,000th day
that we've been apart.

422
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:57,840
February 29th only comes
once every four years.

423
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,560
The last time we had this day,

424
00:39:00,590 --> 00:39:02,190
we even joked that

425
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:04,880
people born on this day are so unlucky

426
00:39:05,710 --> 00:39:09,310
since they can only celebrate
their birthday once every 4 years.

427
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:13,760
June 1st, 2002.

428
00:39:15,590 --> 00:39:16,360
Xia Xue.

429
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:21,240
Last night, I dreamed again
about taking you to the seaside as kids.

430
00:39:22,030 --> 00:39:25,670
We promised we'd go north together
to see the snow someday.

431
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:28,190
I don't know if

432
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:31,000
I still have the chance to do that.

433
00:39:33,280 --> 00:39:33,920
Xia Xue.

434
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:37,630
Today is July 21st, 2005.

435
00:39:37,630 --> 00:39:40,110
Today is January 19th, 2007.

436
00:39:40,110 --> 00:39:40,920
Today is 2009...

437
00:39:40,920 --> 00:39:42,630
Today is your birthday.

438
00:39:43,480 --> 00:39:46,140
I hope everything
always goes smoothly for you,

439
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:48,080
and that you stay safe and sound.

440
00:39:49,880 --> 00:39:50,670
Xia Xue.

441
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,510
I miss you.
